articles.description: Sixth-ranked Cincinnati owns a 15-game winning streak and a three-game lead in the American Athletic Conference standings as it rolls into Dallas to play Southern Methodist on Sunday at Moody Coliseum.

videos.description: Mustapha Heronis goes 4-for-4 from the 3-point line, sinking 16 of Auburn's first 19 points.
videos.headline: Heron hot from 3-point line

videos.description: Auburn's Jared Harper throws the ball across court to Bryce Brown who sinks his third 3-pointer of the day.
videos.headline: Brown drains 3 in transition

videos.description: Desean Murray forces a turnover and gives it off to Jared Harper who  takes it to the rim to draw the 3-point play.
videos.headline: Murray's steal leads to Harper and-1

videos.description: Auburn intercepts an LSU pass and Jared Harper connects with Malik Dunbar alone under the hoop for an alley-oop.
videos.headline: Auburn has some fun on 3-on-0 breakaway

videos.description: Bruce Pearl accidentally hits Jared Harper on the sidelines as he is checking back into the game.
videos.headline: Auburn's Pearl accidentally hits player in face

videos.description: Head coach Bruce Pearl joins SEC Now to talk about Auburn's 11-0 home record and his talented roster.
videos.headline: Pearl: 'These kids are amazing'

videos.description: Mustapha Heron leads the No. 19 Tigers with 21 points and nine rebounds in a 25-point win over LSU.
videos.headline: Auburn dominates LSU

videos.description: Auburn defeats LSU 95-70 and earns its seventh SEC win of the season.
videos.headline: No. 19 Auburn breezes past LSU
